{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-presentation-index-js","path":"/presentations/2018/stress-driven-development/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"cover\"\n        title=\"cover\"\n        src=\"/static/760f821055710ad8b310d81b5682db04/212bf/cover.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/760f821055710ad8b310d81b5682db04/7809d/cover.jpg 192w,\n/static/760f821055710ad8b310d81b5682db04/4ecad/cover.jpg 384w,\n/static/760f821055710ad8b310d81b5682db04/212bf/cover.jpg 768w,\n/static/760f821055710ad8b310d81b5682db04/5ef17/cover.jpg 1152w,\n/static/760f821055710ad8b310d81b5682db04/ac99c/cover.jpg 1536w,\n/static/760f821055710ad8b310d81b5682db04/e1596/cover.jpg 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><strong>Elevator Pitch (~300 words)</strong></p>\n<p>In this talk, we discuss how to manage your day and avoid the daily stressors of any engineering team. The main takeaways of this presentation are how to prevent stress from being accumulated at work and how to organize the work itself in a productive way.</p>\n<p><strong>Presented at</strong></p>\n<br>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://dvinnik.dev/events/2021/craft-conference\">Craft Conference: 2021</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://dvinnik.dev/events/2021/isaqb\">iSAQB Software Architecture Gathering: 2021</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://dvinnik.dev/events/2021/azure-community\">Azure Community Conference: 2021</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://dvinnik.dev/events/2019/agentconf\">AgentConf: 2019</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://dvinnik.dev/events/2019/devoxx-poland\">Devoxx Poland: 2019</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://dvinnik.dev/events/2019/target-quality\">Target Quality: 2019</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://dvinnik.dev/events/2018/geecon-prague\">GeeCon Prague: 2018</a></li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<p><strong>Abstract</strong></p>\n<p>When was the last time you took a day off? How many times this week have you worked overtime? These questions are related to one thing we all experience daily - stress.  Employees trapped by their routine to \"deliver business value at all cost\" often forget to take care of themselves. Unfortunately, this work-related stress affects our loved ones too, because work-life balance that we all hear about, usually means work-life stress.</p>\n<p>What if I were to say that it does not have to be this way? In this talk, we discuss ways how to relax and avoid \"Stress Driven Development.\" We deep dive into everyday stressors, and draft a comprehensive guide to removing stress at work and in our personal lives. </p>\n<p><strong>Takeaways</strong></p>\n<br>\n<ol>\n<li>Outline of everyday work and life stressors</li>\n<li>Guidelines on how to deal with stress </li>\n<li>Tips and Tricks to retain anti-stress practices</li>\n</ol>\n<br>\n<p><strong>Recording</strong></p>\n<br>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ShF8mEzlsEI\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<p><em><a href=\"https://dvinnik.dev/events/2021/craft-conference\">Craft Conference: 2021</a></em></p>\n<br>\n<br>\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nRisoHAnhnA\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<p><em><a href=\"https://dvinnik.dev/events/2018/geecon-prague\">GeeCon Prague: 2018</a></em></p>\n<br>\n<p><strong>Slide Deck</strong></p>\n<br>\n<iframe src=\"//www.slideshare.net/slideshow/embed_code/key/JuVmOUN8ZbvgXs\" width=\"595\" height=\"485\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" style=\"border:1px solid #CCC; border-width:1px; margin-bottom:5px; max-width: 100%;\" allowfullscreen> </iframe> <div style=\"margin-bottom:5px\"> <strong> <a href=\"//www.slideshare.net/DmitryVinnik1/stress-driven-development-and-how-to-avoid-it\" title=\"Stress Driven Development, and How to Avoid It\" target=\"_blank\">Stress Driven Development, and How to Avoid It</a> </strong> from <strong><a href=\"https://www.slideshare.net/DmitryVinnik1\" target=\"_blank\">Dmitry Vinnik</a></strong> </div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Stress Driven Development, and How to Avoid It","date":"Jan 01, 2018"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/presentations/2018/stress-driven-development/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/presentations/2018/uphill-battle-of-mobile-testing/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Uphill Battle of Mobile Visual Regression"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/presentations/2018/leadership-by-example/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Lead by Example Towards Productivity: Science of Lost Time"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2125292342","2915660680","3649515864","63159454"]}